988a1cfe-1493-4262-87a3-8cbfe7f2e7be.3fcc7165-79ca-4cbd-a48f-8adf2341b76e.description=
Compares two strings, returning a true response if and only if they contain the same sequence of characters. A null string is considered to be equal to an empty string.

Inputs\:
string1 - The first string.
string2 - The second string.
ignoreCase - If set to 'true', then the comparison ignores case considerations. The two strings are considered equal ignoring case if they are of the same length and corresponding characters in the two strings are equal ignoring case. If set to any value other than 'true', then the strings must match exactly to be considered equal.

responses\:
true - If the two strings are equal
false - If the two strings are not equal

988a1cfe-1493-4262-87a3-8cbfe7f2e7be.9189fbc9-d721-4ea3-80dd-c6a278634468.description=
This workflow adds the SA Compute based resource offering attached to the infrastructure component to its child server components

Inputs\:

srvList		- CSA Component Id of one or more server (delimited by pipe | operator) on which the SA resource binding is to be created
		  Eg \: ||....
userIdentifier	- CSA User Identifier 
saCompOffrName	- Name of the HP SA offering to be attached to the sever components.
saCompResProviderId	- CSA Resource Provider Id of the HP SA provider to be used by the SA resource binding on the server components

Responses\:
success - Workflow completed successfully.
failure - Something went wrong.

988a1cfe-1493-4262-87a3-8cbfe7f2e7be.description=
This workflow adds the resource bindings for the resource offerings attached to the infrastructure component to its child components, appropriately. It creates resource binding for a uCMDB based resource offering to the sever group components and  resource binding for uCMDB, SiteScope and SA Compute based resource offerings to the server components, if the offering exists on the infrastructure service component.

Inputs\:
srvGrpList		- CSA Component Id of one or more server group (delimited by pipe | operator) on which the uCMDB resource binding is to be created 
		  Eg \: ||....
srvList		- CSA Component Id of one or more server (delimited by pipe | operator) on which the uCMDB, SiteScope, SA resource bindings are to be created
		  Eg \: ||....
userIdentifier	- CSA User Identifier 
infraComponentId	- CSA Component Id of the infrastructure service component. The resource bindings available on this component are attached to its child sever group and server 			  components.

Responses\:
success - Workflow completed successfully.
failure - Something went wrong.
